## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates how **Artificial Intelligence can assist Business Intelligence workflows** by integrating **Claude AI with the Power BI MCP Server**.

The goal was to test how AI can help automate key **Power BI development tasks**, including dataset understanding, data modeling, and DAX measure creation.

By connecting Claude AI to an active **Power BI Desktop session**, the model was able to analyze the dataset and prepare a **dashboard-ready semantic model**.

